caption: If your #naturalhair isn’t “acting right” like it used to you definitely need to make sure you’re clarifying your strands at least monthly. Product build-up can happen even if you wash your hair weekly with a regular shampoo. Strands become dull, lack definition and elasticity, are frizzy, and/or don’t retain moisture. Our #moisturizingblacksoapshampoo is the 🔑 to eliminate it all. This shampoo + using our #locmethod will for sure make your #washday a success!
